Builds or splits a distinguished name specification into components. The class is immutable. The meaning of DN elements:

CN=commonName
OU=organizationUnit
O=organizationName
L=localityName
ST=stateName
C=country

The capitalization does not matter but the order does. Some elements can be omitted from the list
